Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.22,0:00:37.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\ybord0.5}穏やかな日常を
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.02,0:00:38.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\ybord0.5}この地に残して
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.77,0:00:41.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\ybord0.5}時の流れは無情に
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.15,0:00:43.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\ybord0.5}人を忘れさせる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.31,0:00:46.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\ybord0.5}そこに生きた軌跡も
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\ybord0.5}錆び付いていく
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.74,0:00:50.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\ybord0.5}それでも君の
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.03,0:00:51.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\ybord0.5}言葉も願いも勇気も
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.82,0:00:57.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\ybord0.5}今も確かに私の中で生きている
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\ybord0.5}同じ途を選んだ
